profile:
Welcome to A&O Systems Group. We are an established and energetic, consulting and I.T. services company, serving the Canadian and American S.M.B. marketplace, for over ten years, with a combined experience base of over twenty years.

Some of our prestigious clients include Avant Canada and the Law Society of Upper Canada, just to name a couple. Our reach extends far beyond everyday technology which includes niche market areas such as capacity planning, structured cabling service, network and hardware monitoring, storage networks, virtualization, systems security, IP-based telecommunication services, domain name management, web hosting, web design and much more.

The S.M.B., is without question, a rapidly growing market place which is vastly under-served and often cost-prohibitive, for the S.M.B. operator. As a result, our goods and services are highly geared towards this market segment and to help ensure the S.M.B. continued success, in the new global and digital economy.

Our success isn't directly attributed to technology itself, but rather its our service first and complete understanding approach of our clients requirements prior to any project engagement. We strive to understand our clients environment, expectations and align ourselves and technology to meet and exceed those expectations. profile:
IntegrityTeks Inc. was established in 2002 and is a wholly owned and independent Canadian operation. We rebranded in 2013 as part of a deliberate strategy targeted to emphasize the strength of our investment and ongoing commitment to delivering IT services with Integrity and ethics to the Ontario and Canadian market. We believe in using the power of synergy towards providing the best and most reliable service possible. As one of Canada's leading independent full service IT service providers, we offer comprehensive IT services, from computer and network maintenance and support, to setting up wireless offices and designing & development of websites. IntegrityTeks was founded on principles of the power of integrity and synergy. Our operations are based on responsibility, ownership, independent thinking, customer service and teamwork. Our focus is to take care of all your Information Technology and Infrastructure requirements so that you are free to focus on your own business goals. 
IntegrityTeks Inc. isn’t your fly-by-night IT repair & consulting shop.  Our promise is that we will look after ALL your IT needs on time, every time, while exceeding your expectations at a reasonable rate. 
  
Our computer & laptop repair services include: 
•	Diagnostics: Identify the problem and discuss the best possible solution 
•	Hardware Replacement: Diagnose and replace failed hardware such as a hard drive, optical drive, memory, power supply, etc. 
•	Spyware, Malware, and Virus Removal: Scanning and removal of spyware and viruses through specialized software and manual removal 
•	System Optimization: Removing unnecessary and junk files, registry keys, and start-up programs 
•	Upgrades: Upgrade of system memory, hard drive, optical drive, video, sound, and operating systems 
•	Software Configuration: Configuration and optimization of major software applications  
•	Operating System Restoration: Restoring the operating system back onto your hard drive after a system crash or hard drive failure 
•	File Recovery: Many times it is possible to recover important files from a crashed hard drive 
•	Housecalls: We do house calls for both home and business clients 
We have been successfully operating in the Toronto and GTA since the beginning of 2002, and our company will continue to rapidly expand its diverse and specialized range of professional services throughout the region. Our ongoing evolution and intensification of our brand is inevitable. The rebranding of our GTA office is now enabling us to fortify and strengthen our local and national services, accomplish local growth objectives and aggressively foster and develop new client relationships throughout the region. 
Our clients choose IntegrityTeks to be their IT service provider for many reasons including: 
•         Knowledge: IntegrityTeks Inc. brings more than 15 years of experience to their customers 
•         Cost Effectiveness: IntegrityTeks Inc. services are cost effective for both small business and residences 
•         Customer Service Support: 24/7 support is available with high turnaround time in response to solving issues 
•         Customization: IntegrityTeks solutions and services are highly customizable -we work for you 
•         Security and Privacy: Your information is secure with us, and we treat your privacy with the utmost respect 
•         Environmentally and Socially Conscious: We take our responsibility to the protection of our environment serious 
  
 Most importantly, however, IntegrityTeks suggests a solution only when it can add value to your organization and circumstance.
You may visit our website at http://IntegrityTeks.com
